ise as a martyr. In fact he has done nothing more than gather other cowardly people who believe that they can achieve power even in death and convince them that their killing innocents is not the act of a coward. For those of us living in diverse areas, its important to remember that those around you arab, palastinian, muslim and alike are not the enemy. They as a whole are not responsible for this tragedy. And im certain their horror and shock is not only equal but maybe surpasses ours in the knowledge than a fellow countryman could hold such disdain for human life.<br><br>The one who planned, lead and executed this, YOU are the one to be held accountable, to face the full wrath of the combined people of America. You alone will face her fury and God will not have mercy on your soul. <p>     Ravenark <BR>52nd season Cavalier <BR></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub54.ezboard.com/ulorddrunkeness.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lord Drunkeness</A> at: 9/11/01 6:08:20 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub54.ezboard.com/uxocinve.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XocinVE</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>the bucket-head</span><br>  Posts: 100<br> <font color=#00CCFF>(9/11/01 6:21:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=212.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.voodooextreme.com/billy/tshirts/brian%20dugan/veshirt.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Reflection upon todays tragedy.</span><hr size=1> Well said Rav, well fuxin said.. <p><B><Center>Xocin, 60 Warlord </b></center><br><b>Before you judge a person, walk a mile in their shoes, than you'll be a mile away, and have their shoes</b><br><i><b>"The walking billboard of ad